title.rendered: STEDI 2.0M WIRING EXTENSION CABLE DEUTSCH DT CONNECTOR STEDI LIGHT HARNESS

content.rendered:
2.0m Extension Cable with Seal DT connector

OVERVIEW

For those looking for some extra length to wire up driving/work lights fitted around the car. Available in DT and DTP in 2000mm environmentally sealed cable.

PLUG & PLAY

Male & Female plugs for running directly from the harness and straight into the back of your lights.

COMPATABILITY

Compatible with all wiring harnesses for LED, HID and Halogen Lights that run a DT connector. Make sure you are familiar with DT & DTP connectors as they are not cross-compatible with one another.

DETAILS

Listing is for 2.0m DT Version

2.0m Extension Cable compatible with all wiring kits fitted with the Deutsch sealed DT and DTP connectors.

Please be aware that we have two varieties of the Deutsch connector, to ensure you are buying the correct one please refer to the attached image.

We generally use the smaller Deutsch DT connector for all light bars up to and including 200w, and the larger DTP connector is used for light bars beyond.

SPECIFICATIONS

  • 2.0m Cable
  • Waterproof DT Connectors
  • Cable placed inside conduit

 

WHAT’S IN THE BOX

  • 2.0m DT wiring harness extension lead
